titlestmt.titleproper: Guide to the Commercial Paper Sample Book Collection
titlestmt.author: Compiled by Arts of the Book Staff

profiledesc.creation: This finding aid was produced using ArchivesSpace on Saturday December 8, 2018 at 00:00

did.abstract: The collection comprises sample books from primarily American commercial paper manufacturers.

accessrestrict.head: Conditions Governing Access
accessrestrict.p: The materials are open for research.

userestrict.head: Conditions Governing Use
userestrict.p: Copyright has not been transferred to Yale University.

prefercite.head: Preferred Citation
prefercite.p: Commercial Paper Sample Book Collection, Robert B. Haas Family Arts Library, Yale University.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: The collection comprises sample books from primarily American commercial paper manufacturers. The sample books employ a variety of binding formats and showcase a range of paper styles, weights, and colors.

arrangement.head: Arrangement
arrangement.p: The collection is arranged alphabetically by manufacturer.

arrangement.head: Arrangement
arrangement.p: Arranged alphabetically by manufacturer. See also oversize listing.
